e Wightmanhad been in 2022 when holding off God's gift down the stretch.\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999996971383, \"rank\": 3.0305878131672174e-10, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"defeat\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"the ego monster\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"illness\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"simply the next man\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"line\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"Britain'sJake Wightmanhad\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"God's gift\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 862}, {\"ngram\": \"the stretch\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The alternative view, expressed by Kerr, is that Ingebrigtsen needs to be led along by pacemakers to crank out the victories with the regularity he does.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The alternative view\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"pacemakers\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"the victories\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"the regularity\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This does not happen at major championships where the qualifying rounds filter out the domestiques.\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1134, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"major championships\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualifying\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"the domestiques\", \"from\